{"title":"七律五首  读陈毅副总理在中外记者招待会谈话有感","authors":["王力"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七律五首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读陈毅副总理在中外记者招待会谈话有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪言壮语最强音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道出神州六亿心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主义环球瞻北斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政权新国有南针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声波远撼摩天厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心瓣遥呈椰树林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努目低眉分敌我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔诅咒友朋钦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊千年绵亘长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心何事学强梁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条道路由君择，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九万平方是我疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有礼当知仍有节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能柔应识亦能刚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只轮匹马前车鉴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黩武从无好下场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生财自诩兴家早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作态相怜创业难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若不因人肠辘辘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何由使汝面团团！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥涂此日翻身起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云路他年刮目看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世道沧桑应记取，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗟来莫漫舍三餐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情翘首望南天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此英雄如此坚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤帜迎风招义烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河汲水洗腥羶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亡秦岂止存三户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝长宜站一边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行见铁蹄清扫尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯歌万里净烽烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒吼共工触不周，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国魂叱咤唤神州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焚心久积填膺愤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺背深铭刻骨仇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日一轮驱雾夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青松六亿斗霜秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长蛇封豕终灰烬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树帜昆仑最上头。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}